<H3> <TI>   Australia Spends $6.5 Million To Train Pilots </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Australia Spends $6.5 Million To Train Pilots </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2305115094 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 21 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2305115094 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Australia Minister for Development and Cooperation 
Mr. Gordon Bilney has announced a grant of $6.5 million to train 
60 Vietnamese pilots over several years to fly modern jet 
aircraft. A delegation from Vietnam, led by Vietnam Airlines 
Human Resources Development Manager Nguyen Sy Hung, recently 
visited Adelaide for discussion with Qantas and the Australian 
Aviation College. 

</TEXT>

