<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Osaka, May 23 KYODO -- The Kansai Economic 
Federation (Kankeiren) on Monday [23 May] appointed Tetsuro 
Kawakami as its chairman to succeed Osamu Uno, who is retiring. 
