  [Text] Organizations, plants, and enterprises in Pyongyang 
are actively supporting the People's Army soldiers who are 
striving for socialist construction. 
  On 20 May, functionaries and working people from over 120 
units of organizations, including Pyongyang municipal people's 
committee and Pyongyang municipal administrative economic 
committee, plants and enterprises, and education sector visited 
