people- army unity by actively supporting and taking good care 
of the fighters of the supreme commander Comrade Kim Chong-il, 
congratulated and encouraged the soldiers' labor achievement by 
visiting the construction site with more than 220 automobiles 
loaded with tens of thousands of over 60 kinds of relief goods. 

